'''The Warren''', also known simply as the '''Imperial Research Facility''', was a top-secret [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] military research facility on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

{{Struct-stub}}

==History==
{{Quote|The Empire has conducted many top secret operations at this location. Unfortunately, it has been very difficult to penetrate the defenses of the Warren on our side.|[[Adar Tallon/Legends|Adar Tallon]], to a Rebel operative|<ref name="SWG:AT">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=other|Corellian Corvette Pre-Quest: "Adar Tallon"}}</ref>}}
During the years surrounding [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], the Warren was commanded by [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Bors Teraud]]. According to rumor, under Teraud's command, a rogue scientist experimented in genetics, cybernetics and brain translation to create an army of cyborgs loyal to Teraud with the plan of overthrowing [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. The same rumors claim that the project failed when Teraud's scientist turned the cyborgs against the officer. When word of Teraud's fate reached the ears of his superiors, a spacer was hired to enter the Warren, gather evidence of the experiment and return it to his employers.

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]],<ref name="SWG_timeline">{{SWG_timeline}}</ref> a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] officer [[Adar Tallon/Legends|Adar Tallon]] dispatched an operative to the facility in order to retrieve the security override codes of a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|Corellian corvette]] that was carrying a captured highly-decorated [[Rebel pilot/Legends|Alliance pilot]].<ref name="SWG:AT" />

==Behind the scenes==
The Warren appeared in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Star Wars video games|massively multiplayer online role-playing game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]],<ref name="SWG:TW" /> prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref> The Warren was added to the game with the "[[W:c:swg:Publish 3 Notes: 8 October 03|Publish 3]]," released on [[October 8]], 2003.<ref name="SonyCite-Publish 3: The Warren">{{SonyCite|url=recent_updates.jsp?o=60890|text=Publish 3: The Warren}}</ref>

